<div class="container place" style="background-color:aliceblue;border-radius:5px;padding:40px;">
    <h3 class="place" style="color:darkcyan;font-family:Quicksand;">What is PURPOSE?</h3>
    <p style="font-size:small;font-family:'Segoe UI';">
        Purpose is a Non Profit Organization that aims to preserve, save and increase marine life expetency.
        It is an organization that tries to build against the effects of Climate Change to enable sea life growth and also protect endangered marine species.
        We are not only looking out for sea and ocean life, but also fresh water life, the cleanliness of its environment and the growth of a habitable ecosystem that different species can coexist in.
        By taking care of these animals and making sure they are well and are growing progressively towards a healthy population that continues to effect our planet for the better.
        For this goal of ours to succeed we use innovative technology to solve researche proven solutions or creating new methods for old processes. With a loving team such as ours, we have reached many successes over the years that have proved fruitful for our cause.
        Each and every employee acknowledges their mission and goal, knowing they in turn are valued and their safety is always first. We appreciate their work and efforts to bring more stability in our waters.
        Making fishes very happy is our largest accomplishment thus far.
        Check our @Html.ActionLink("Process & Aim", "Aim", "Aim") page to know more about our methods, aims and how we run things.
    </p>
</div>
